<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: The chance this creature will attack when harmed.\n\nThis chance increases up to three times if the attacker is closer.\n\nThis chance is applied each time damage is taken. This means that slower-firing, higher-damage weapons are less likely to trigger it while hunting. -->
  <ManhunterOnDamageChance.headerTip>此生物在受到攻擊時觸發的反擊率。\n\n攻擊者越近，觸發機率越大，最高可增加三倍。\n每次受到傷害時都有機率會觸發，所以射速慢、傷害高的武器在狩獵時更不容易觸發。</ManhunterOnDamageChance.headerTip>
  
  <!-- EN: The chance that this creature will attack when a tamer tries to tame it and fails. -->
  <ManhunterOnTameFailChance.headerTip>馴獸師嘗試馴服生物失敗時，生物進行反擊的機率。</ManhunterOnTameFailChance.headerTip>
  
</LanguageData>